channel.title: Moparscape server ip and port problem
channel.description:
As i bore of being by my self, i see the light. Mabye there are more people. :D
As i search the web for people to join i realise there is a server button on top of moparscape page. -.-
i go through most of the servers, but moparscape says "Error connecting to server. Must be down." so i go to the forms and look around and fine about 6,000,000,000 people with the same problem as me.
So i decide to go find a video on how to get it to work. and guess what. 6,000,000,000 people have videos sayin they cant get on.
So i beg of you my fellow moparscapians, [size=25pt] "please tell me how to work this crazy thing!" [/size] :(
